description: Some residents have still not returned to their homes in Laxey after last October's major flooding.
title: Flood aid for Laxey residents 'chicken feed', says MHK
title_page: Flood aid for Laxey residents 'chicken feed', says MHK - BBC News
maintext: More than 60 properties were damaged during the flooding after water spilled through a hole in the river wall which was being used as an access point for works.
